{"tid":2296403,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李克強：要創造更多就業崗位 有就業 有收入 就有消費","createTime":"2020-11-22T12:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T13:39:44.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83787a9c5e942c0eb68146a84174c14a3e7c8f71","tid":2296403,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"李克強：要創造更多就業崗位<br />\n<br />\n總理李克強主持召開部分地方政府負責人視頻座談會，指今年面對巨大挑戰，但疫情防控取得重大戰略成果，經濟較快實現恢復性正增長。他指出，要充分認識當前國內外形勢依然複雜嚴峻、存在很大不確定性，要保持政策連續性、有效性和可持續性，著力穩就業、擴內需，指「有就業有收入就有消費」，要強化就業優先政策，創造更多就業崗位。<br />\n<br />\n李克強又強調，要堅持改革開放，上億市場主體是穩增長、保就業的基礎，要打造市場化、法治化、國際化營商環境，推動高水平對外開放，做好穩外貿穩外資工作，穩定產業鏈供應鏈。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2367386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2367386&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=2b26df7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2367386</a>"},{"pid":"19247cf99fcb7cb26e0b3ec423c91dff51311df9","tid":2296403,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"有多啲雞就有多啲蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁啲雞邊度黎"},{"pid":"158a3466f82a4176085cf96edbdc529d72ab69d6","tid":2296403,"uid":111322,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"重啟莞式iso文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e84c19fea532158496d26be0c6bd865aaa7cf2","tid":2296403,"uid":61994,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:40:58.000Z","msg":"阿媽係女人，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bea56f28d2dc50ade86aca2b9944a075e73d291","tid":2296403,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158a3466f82a4176085cf96edbdc529d72ab69d6","tid":2296403,"uid":111322,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:40:19.000Z","msg":"重啟莞式iso文化<im